data.name: label2.Text
data.value: This is Kropiner. He is a very responsible fuzzy. He looks after the small creatures - the kropik. They are very playful and restless, but because they are still very small - they can fall asleep at any moment. Fuzzy wants to find them all and return them to their mothers. Help him! As soon as you realize that in the cell kropik - put the flag. The game will end, when you find all the kids (put the flags), then Fuzzy can return them home immediately.
